data.description: Buyer got cold feet, now it's your opportunity! This end-unit townhome lives larger than its size! Featuring beamed vaulted ceilings, luxury vinyl plank flooring, a roomy kitchen with stainless steel appliances and maintenance-free deck. The primary bedroom is a true retreat with a walk-in closet and vanity counter and sink. The lower level is spacious and perfect for guests, with a family room, third bedroom, and 3/4 bath. The yard provides privacy and the chance to create your ideal landscaping! Updates include: Roof-2017, Siding-2021, New a/c, water heater, furnace main command board.
